Twitzkrieg: Real-time Twitter aggregator that uses the Streaming API. (Requires Tweetstream, and Beautiful Soup modules)

python Twitzkrieg.py [twitter_account_username] [twitter_account_password] [output_file_for_tweets] [script_runtime_in_hours] [script_runtime_in_minutes]

example: python Twitzkrieg.py test testpsd test.txt 7 10 #Run script for 7 hours, 10 minutes, and output tweets into test.txt

Script will then prompt user for search predicates separated by commas (example: elections,vuvuzela,oil-spill)


